{"repository_name":"read_until","body":"# read_until.cr\n\n[![Test](https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/actions/workflows/test.yml/badge.svg)](https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/actions/workflows/test.yml)\n[![Lines of Code](https://img.shields.io/endpoint?url=https%3A%2F%2Ftokei.kojix2.net%2Fbadge%2Fgithub%2Fkojix2%2Fread_until%2Flines)](https://tokei.kojix2.net/github/kojix2/read_until)\n\n🕳️⚡ Oxford Nanopore [Read Until](https://github.com/nanoporetech/read_until_api) - for [Crystal](https://crystal-lang.org/)\n\n## Installation\n\nAdd the dependency to your shard.yml:\n\n```yaml\ndependencies:\n  read_until:\n    github: kojix2/read_until\n```\n\nRun `shards install`\n\n## Usage\n\n```crystal\nrequire \"read_until\"\n```\n\nRun example:\n\n```sh\ncrystal run examples/basic.cr\n```\n\nExpected output shape:\n\n```text\nendpoint=<host:port>\nrunning=true\nlatest_read_id=<read-id>\nqueued_actions=<n>\n```\n\n## Development\n\n- Your contributions and feedback are welcome\n- This library was generated by an AI agent based on human instructions.\n\n## License\n\nThis project is distributed under the Mozilla Public License 2.0 (MPL-2.0).\n\nIt includes a Crystal port of Oxford Nanopore's Python `read_until_api` and\ninherits the upstream license requirements for derived source files.\n\n- Project license: [LICENSE](LICENSE)\n- Upstream project: https://github.com/nanoporetech/read_until_api\n- Upstream license text: https://github.com/nanoporetech/read_until_api/blob/release/LICENSE.md\n","program":{"html_id":"read_until/toplevel","path":"toplevel.html","kind":"module","full_name":"Top Level Namespace","name":"Top Level Namespace","abstract":false,"locations":[],"repository_name":"read_until","program":true,"enum":false,"alias":false,"const":false,"types":[{"html_id":"read_until/ReadUntil","path":"ReadUntil.html","kind":"module","full_name":"ReadUntil","name":"ReadUntil","abstract":false,"locations":[{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":4,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L4"},{"filename":"src/read_until/version.cr","line_number":1,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until/version.cr#L1"}],"repository_name":"read_until","program":false,"enum":false,"alias":false,"const":false,"constants":[{"id":"Client","name":"Client","value":"ReadUntilClient"},{"id":"VERSION","name":"VERSION","value":"{{ (`shards version /home/runner/work/read_until/read_until/src/read_until`).chomp.stringify }}"}],"types":[{"html_id":"read_until/ReadUntil/ReadCache","path":"ReadUntil/ReadCache.html","kind":"class","full_name":"ReadUntil::ReadCache","name":"ReadCache","abstract":false,"superclass":{"html_id":"read_until/Reference","kind":"class","full_name":"Reference","name":"Reference"},"ancestors":[{"html_id":"read_until/Reference","kind":"class","full_name":"Reference","name":"Reference"},{"html_id":"read_until/Object","kind":"class","full_name":"Object","name":"Object"}],"locations":[{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":38,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L38"}],"repository_name":"read_until","program":false,"enum":false,"alias":false,"const":false,"namespace":{"html_id":"read_until/ReadUntil","kind":"module","full_name":"ReadUntil","name":"ReadUntil"},"doc":"Thread-safe bounded cache keyed by channel.\n\nKeeps the most recent chunk per channel up to *size* total entries.\nWhen full, the oldest entry (by insertion order) is evicted.\n`.missed`   — reads evicted before consumption (distinct read replaced).\n`.replaced` — chunks overwritten by a later chunk of the same read.","summary":"<p>Thread-safe bounded cache keyed by channel.</p>","constructors":[{"html_id":"new(size:Int32=512)-class-method","name":"new","abstract":false,"args":[{"name":"size","default_value":"512","external_name":"size","restriction":"Int32"}],"args_string":"(size : Int32 = 512)","args_html":"(size : Int32 = <span class=\"n\">512</span>)","location":{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":43,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L43"},"def":{"name":"new","args":[{"name":"size","default_value":"512","external_name":"size","restriction":"Int32"}],"visibility":"Public","body":"_ = allocate\n_.initialize(size)\nif _.responds_to?(:finalize)\n  ::GC.add_finalizer(_)\nend\n_\n"},"external_var":false}],"instance_methods":[{"html_id":"[]=(channel:Int32,chunk:ReadChunk):ReadChunk-instance-method","name":"[]=","abstract":false,"args":[{"name":"channel","external_name":"channel","restriction":"Int32"},{"name":"chunk","external_name":"chunk","restriction":"ReadChunk"}],"args_string":"(channel : Int32, chunk : ReadChunk) : ReadChunk","args_html":"(channel : Int32, chunk : <a href=\"../ReadUntil/ReadChunk.html\">ReadChunk</a>) : <a href=\"../ReadUntil/ReadChunk.html\">ReadChunk</a>","location":{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":54,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L54"},"def":{"name":"[]=","args":[{"name":"channel","external_name":"channel","restriction":"Int32"},{"name":"chunk","external_name":"chunk","restriction":"ReadChunk"}],"return_type":"ReadChunk","visibility":"Public","body":"@mutex.synchronize do\n  if @data.has_key?(channel)\n    existing = @data[channel]\n    if existing.id == chunk.id\n      @replaced = @replaced + 1\n    else\n      @missed = @missed + 1\n    end\n    @order.delete(channel)\n  elsif @data.size >= @size\n    evicted = @order.shift\n    @data.delete(evicted)\n    @missed = @missed + 1\n  end\n  @data[channel] = chunk\n  @order << channel\nend\nchunk\n"},"external_var":false},{"html_id":"[]?(channel:Int32):ReadChunk|Nil-instance-method","name":"[]?","abstract":false,"args":[{"name":"channel","external_name":"channel","restriction":"Int32"}],"args_string":"(channel : Int32) : ReadChunk | Nil","args_html":"(channel : Int32) : <a href=\"../ReadUntil/ReadChunk.html\">ReadChunk</a> | Nil","location":{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":50,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L50"},"def":{"name":"[]?","args":[{"name":"channel","external_name":"channel","restriction":"Int32"}],"return_type":"ReadChunk | ::Nil","visibility":"Public","body":"@mutex.synchronize do @data[channel]? end"},"external_var":false},{"html_id":"clear:Nil-instance-method","name":"clear","abstract":false,"location":{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":104,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L104"},"def":{"name":"clear","return_type":"Nil","visibility":"Public","body":"@mutex.synchronize do @data.clear\n@order.clear\n end"},"external_var":false},{"html_id":"current_size:Int32-instance-method","name":"current_size","abstract":false,"location":{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":100,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L100"},"def":{"name":"current_size","return_type":"Int32","visibility":"Public","body":"@mutex.synchronize do @data.size end"},"external_var":false},{"html_id":"delete(channel:Int32):ReadChunk|Nil-instance-method","name":"delete","abstract":false,"args":[{"name":"channel","external_name":"channel","restriction":"Int32"}],"args_string":"(channel : Int32) : ReadChunk | Nil","args_html":"(channel : Int32) : <a href=\"../ReadUntil/ReadChunk.html\">ReadChunk</a> | Nil","location":{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":75,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L75"},"def":{"name":"delete","args":[{"name":"channel","external_name":"channel","restriction":"Int32"}],"return_type":"ReadChunk | ::Nil","visibility":"Public","body":"@mutex.synchronize do\n  chunk = @data.delete(channel)\n  if chunk\n    @order.delete(channel)\n  end\n  chunk\nend"},"external_var":false},{"html_id":"missed:Int32-instance-method","name":"missed","abstract":false,"location":{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":40,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L40"},"def":{"name":"missed","return_type":"Int32","visibility":"Public","body":"@missed"},"external_var":false},{"html_id":"pop(count:Int32=1,newest_first:Bool=true):Array(Tuple(Int32,ReadChunk))-instance-method","name":"pop","doc":"Removes and returns up to *count* chunks from the cache.\nBy default returns the newest entries first.","summary":"<p>Removes and returns up to <em>count</em> chunks from the cache.</p>","abstract":false,"args":[{"name":"count","default_value":"1","external_name":"count","restriction":"Int32"},{"name":"newest_first","default_value":"true","external_name":"newest_first","restriction":"Bool"}],"args_string":"(count : Int32 = 1, newest_first : Bool = true) : Array(Tuple(Int32, ReadChunk))","args_html":"(count : Int32 = <span class=\"n\">1</span>, newest_first : Bool = <span class=\"n\">true</span>) : Array(Tuple(Int32, <a href=\"../ReadUntil/ReadChunk.html\">ReadChunk</a>))","location":{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":85,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L85"},"def":{"name":"pop","args":[{"name":"count","default_value":"1","external_name":"count","restriction":"Int32"},{"name":"newest_first","default_value":"true","external_name":"newest_first","restriction":"Bool"}],"return_type":"Array(::Tuple(Int32, ReadChunk))","visibility":"Public","body":"@mutex.synchronize do\n  result = [] of ::Tuple(Int32, ReadChunk)\n  count.times do\n    key = newest_first ? @order.last? : @order.first?\n    if key\n    else\n      break\n    end\n    chunk = @data.delete(key)\n    if chunk\n    else\n      break\n    end\n    @order.delete(key)\n    result << {key, chunk}\n  end\n  result\nend"},"external_var":false},{"html_id":"replaced:Int32-instance-method","name":"replaced","abstract":false,"location":{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":41,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L41"},"def":{"name":"replaced","return_type":"Int32","visibility":"Public","body":"@replaced"},"external_var":false},{"html_id":"size:Int32-instance-method","name":"size","abstract":false,"location":{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":39,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L39"},"def":{"name":"size","return_type":"Int32","visibility":"Public","body":"@size"},"external_var":false}]},{"html_id":"read_until/ReadUntil/ReadChunk","path":"ReadUntil/ReadChunk.html","kind":"class","full_name":"ReadUntil::ReadChunk","name":"ReadChunk","abstract":false,"superclass":{"html_id":"read_until/Reference","kind":"class","full_name":"Reference","name":"Reference"},"ancestors":[{"html_id":"read_until/Reference","kind":"class","full_name":"Reference","name":"Reference"},{"html_id":"read_until/Object","kind":"class","full_name":"Object","name":"Object"}],"locations":[{"filename":"src/read_until.cr","line_number":9,"url":"https://github.com/kojix2/read_until/blob/01cf9b210f3c834de3e3f8b95a17bb2a1b39c4d8/src/read_until.cr#L9"}],"repository_name":"read_until","program":false,"enum":false,"alias":false,"const":false,"namespace":{"html_id":"read_until/ReadUntil","kind":"module","full_name":"ReadUntil","name":"ReadUntil"},"doc":"A single chunk of raw signal data delivered from MinKNOW.\n\nField names follow `GetLiveReadsResponse::ReadData`.\n`channel` is the map key from the response, injected by the client.","summary":"<p>A single chunk of raw signal data delivered from MinKNOW.</p>","constructors":[{"html_id":"new(channel:Int32,id:String,chunk_star